Sentencas: Bi doping of SrFeO(3-delta) results in the formation of a structure with high symmetry and extraordinary electrochemical performance for Bi(0.5)Sr(0.5)FeO(3-delta), which is capable of competing effectively with the current Co-based cathode benchmark with additional advantages of lower thermal expansion and cost.
Titulo: High performance cobalt-free perovskite cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
